{"pageProps":{"article":{"id":"2355f5a973","title":"红军东征的任务","origin":"","is_range_date":false,"dates":[{"id":"a8cb6b4049","index":0,"year":1936,"month":2,"day":18,"articleId":"2355f5a973"}],"tags":[{"id":"c9f57d6426","name":"文章","type":"文稿类型"},{"id":"dd2b275f6c","name":"毛泽东","type":"人物"}],"aliases":[],"publications":[{"id":"maoquanji8","name":"毛泽东全集第8卷","internal":false,"official":false,"type":"pdf","author":"张迪杰","files":"https://raw.githubusercontent.com/banned-historical-archives/banned-historical-archives8/main/mao-quanji/maoquanji8.pdf"}],"authors":[{"id":"261e5467ec","name":"毛泽东"}]},"publication_details":{"maoquanji8":{"comments":[],"contents":[{"id":"4e60ffc6bf","type":"paragraph","text":"红军东征的任务”","index":0,"publicationId":"maoquanji8","articleId":"2355f5a973"},{"id":"2ee4df3a40","type":"paragraph","text":"（1936年2月18日）东征的任务有三项：一是到外线打击卖国贼图锡山，并调动他在陕北的四个旅的兵力，借以粉碎敌人对陕甘边区新的“围”：二是配合北平“一二·九”学生抗日爱国运动和全国反内战高潮：三是壮大自己的力量，促进抗日民族统一战线的实现当前我们的首要任务是渡过黄河。[1]1936年2月18日，毛泽东出席红一方而军团以上干部会议，作关于东征形势与任务的报告。这是报告的一部分。","index":1,"publicationId":"maoquanji8","articleId":"2355f5a973"}],"page":{"id":"97f63697e8","publicationId":"maoquanji8","articleId":"2355f5a973","start":236,"end":236}}}},"__N_SSG":true}